Interface LogsInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DJavaHook, LogsImpl

    public interface LogsInterface
    Encapsulates abstract logging or other reporting activity allowing for different outlets of test logging and reporting.
    Author:
    Carl Nagle, SAS Institute, Inc.
